works.description:
Dear Google Technicians,

I own an e-shop, through which I sell seeds in Czech Republic and
Slovakia. My competitor copied texts and articles from my page. I hold
copyright to these works. He posted these texts on third party pages
and also created a twin of my page.

The search results are polluted by these copied texts. My page rank
went from first rank on first page to third page. As a result, the
amount of orders through my e-shop dropped.

I have secured evidence about all these facts.

Please can you delete the infringing websites from the index? The
infringing websites are:
